@node Main "TriOtix - Documentation"

                              'TriOtix' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'TriOtix' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} played on a triangular shaped
board. The idea is to move a coloured bar from the highest position,
to the exit at the lower position, where a small square is located.
The game board is filled with 24 bars, including the coloured bar,
each occupying two spaces. An empty space, indicated by a small dot,
is placed somewhere on the game board.

  Complete the game in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

